{"tid":673621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"食偉哥可以醫Cancer！？","createTime":"2018-05-22T04:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T06:38:53.000Z","uid":40072,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"eb81f7e44bcc07be78b0ede0da84429764c90a76","tid":673621,"uid":40072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:05:32.000Z","msg":"加拿大癌症最新研究　「威而鋼」配流感疫苗可除9成癌細胞　<br />\n<br />\n癌症奪命，加拿大最新研究發現，治療男性勃起功能障礙的藥物「威而鋼」及「犀利士」，配合流感疫苗，可有效幫助免疫系統清除手術後逾90%殘留的癌細胞，研究結果已刊登於國際期刊《腫瘤免疫學》（OncoImmunology），並正接受評核，看看是否可逐步應用在世界臨床試驗。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大渥太華大學（University of Ottawa）研究團隊發表的最新研究報告顯示，治療男性勃起功能障礙的藥物、包括威而鋼（Viagra）及犀利士（Ciali），配合流感疫苗「Agriflu」使用，可有效幫助免疫系統清除手術後留下的癌細胞。<br />\n<br />\n領導有關研究的渥太華大學醫學院腫瘤專家Dr. Rebecca Auer表示，目前手術可有效移除腫瘤，但與此同時，手術亦會壓抑免疫系統，令剩餘的癌細胞可繼續生存、並向身體其他器官擴散。而他們的研究顯示，威而鋼等藥物卻可阻斷手術後人體產生的免疫細胞「myeloid derived suppressor cells (MDSC)」，防止癌細胞擴散及轉移。<br />\n<br />\n研究團隊發現，在患轉移性癌症的老鼠實驗中，手術後平均癌細胞數量為120個；但如果將威而鋼（Viagra）、犀利士（Ciali）及流感疫苗「Agriflu」給合，應用在老鼠身上時，平均癌細胞數量大降至11個，若不加入流感疫苗治療，癌細胞數量亦下趺至24個。<br />\n<br />\nDr. Rebecca Auer正在於24位胃癌患者身上、進行全球首次臨床實驗，期望可獲進一步實證支持；她認為，若這安全且相對便宜的療法、經臨床試驗獲證實，將成為全球首個「針對癌症手術後引發免疫系統問題」的治療，但她強調，癌症患者不宜自行服食有關藥物，應與醫生商討。<br />\n<br />\n本港臨床腫瘤科專科醫生傅惠霖表示，有關研究結果與現行治療方法，比如化療、免疫療法截然不同，認為如能得到進一步實證支持，將是一個突破。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2077524/加拿大癌症最新研究%E3%80%80「威而鋼」配流感疫苗可除9成癌細胞%E3%80%80%E3%80%80?r=cpsdfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2077524%2F%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E7%99%8C%E7%97%87%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%25E3%2580%2580%E3%80%8C%E5%A8%81%E8%80%8C%E9%8B%BC%E3%80%8D%E9%85%8D%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E5%8F%AF%E9%99%A49%E6%88%90%E7%99%8C%E7%B4%B0%E8%83%9E%25E3%2580%2580%25E3%2580%2580%3Fr%3Dcpsdfb&d=odoMKt4dcH3os18d4Fupb8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=f6f10724\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2077524/加拿大癌症最新研究%E3%80%80「威而鋼」配流感疫苗可除9成癌細胞%E3%80%80%E3%80%80?r=cpsdfb</a><br />\n <br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n偉哥真係用途廣泛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a33ea1606ad27e2be3ae94abcb67d68d098bed6","tid":673621,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:07:18.000Z","msg":"長期扯旗咁點？"},{"pid":"db87ac087dd0b0b8eca5ba9b9661ed08403c4f9d","tid":673621,"uid":20222,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:08:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201712/2764cab733c89b7757dd009747a3166c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201712%2F2764cab733c89b7757dd009747a3166c.JPG&h=d939d70e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗起依張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eda7e0f62bc8fa2e4d7267f6b7cca53a9aa4f26","tid":673621,"uid":63414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a33ea1606ad27e2be3ae94abcb67d68d098bed6","tid":673621,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:07:18.000Z","msg":"長期扯旗咁點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:09:02.000Z","msg":"打丁"},{"pid":"291b721d96f6a12bfd1bce10f73b81a4e567311f","tid":673621,"uid":40072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a33ea1606ad27e2be3ae94abcb67d68d098bed6","tid":673621,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:07:18.000Z","msg":"長期扯旗咁點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:09:43.000Z","msg":"咁應該變賓洲癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846214e8aec5ade058e8f069ec811f3bc4b1ce3e","tid":673621,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"